<node id="SH的KVstore狀態測試環境">
  <data key="d0">SH的KVstore狀態測試環境</data>
  <data key="d1">equipment</data>
  <data key="d2">The testing environment for SH's KVstore status is used to diagnose and resolve issues related to the KVstore engine in a controlled setting.</data>
