  <data key="d2">Tenable API App integration is an ongoing task aimed at connecting Tenable’s platform with existing systems for better security management.&lt;SEP&gt;Tenable API App串接is a task related to integrating Tenable API application.&lt;SEP&gt;Task involving integration of the Tenable API application with B客戶's systems.&lt;SEP&gt;這是一項將進行中的任務，旨在連接和整合Tenable的API應用程序，以提升安全性和監控功能。&lt;SEP&gt;Planning the integration of Tenable API App, pending further implementation.</data>
