  <data key="d2">CentOS操作系统升级是一项正在评估中的维护任务。&lt;SEP&gt;CentOS操作系统升级是指对CentOS系统的更新活动，目前处于评估阶段。&lt;SEP&gt;Centos作業系統升級refers to an ongoing assessment for upgrading CentOS operating system.&lt;SEP&gt;Centos作業系統升級is an ongoing evaluation and planning task aimed at upgrading CentOS systems for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;An upgrade task for the CentOS operating system, currently under evaluation.</data>
