<edge source="E客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">20.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C人員, E客戶) refers to a relationship where C人員 performs various maintenance activities and responsibilities for E客戶. This includes handling maintenance tasks assigned according to work orders, addressing issues as they arise, and providing ongoing support services. For instance, on December 9, 2025, C人員 provided maintenance services to E客戶, and also conducted several tasks related to E客户的maintenance on December 2, 2025.

The responsibilities of C人員 extend beyond routine maintenance tasks; they are also tasked with providing engineering support tailored to meet the needs of Eお客様. This involves ensuring that their systems operate smoothly and any issues are promptly resolved. The relationship is characterized by consistent service delivery and a proactive approach to maintaining system functionality and reliability for E客戶.

In addition, C人員's duties encompass technical support alongside maintenance activities. These tasks aim at maintaining the operational integrity and efficiency of E客户的systems, including regular service provision and task performance at specified dates and times. 

Overall, E客户works closely with C人员on various maintenance tasks to ensure smooth operation and timely resolution of any issues that arise. The relationship emphasizes a collaborative effort in sustaining system reliability and functionality for E客戶 through comprehensive maintenance services provided by C人員.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員performed system maintenance tasks on behalf of E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶received maintenance services provided by C人員.&lt;SEP&gt;C personnel is responsible for conducting the maintenance work on behalf of E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provided maintenance services for E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶receives maintenance services from C人員.</data>
  <data key="d9">client-engineer relationship,client-service,collaboration,customer-engineer relationship,engineer-client relationship,engineering service,engineering support,maintenance,maintenance service provision,maintenance support,maintenance tasks,maintenance work,responsibility,service delivery,service provision,support,task assignment,task execution</data>
