<edge source="C人員" target="B客戶">
  <data key="d7">14.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C人员, B客户) refers to a relationship where C人员 (the designated engineer) performs various maintenance and technical support tasks for B客户. This includes handling routine maintenance activities, addressing specific system issues such as hard disk space saturation and data synchronization problems, and providing overall technical support. Additionally, C人员 collaborates with A人员 on these maintenance efforts and receives monthly reports from Splunk to facilitate the coordination of related work.

C人员 is responsible for conducting regular maintenance tasks for B客户, ensuring that all systems are running smoothly. This role involves not only addressing immediate issues but also monitoring system health and performance continuously. Furthermore, C人员 plays a critical part in maintaining communication with other team members involved in B客户的 support, such as receiving and acting upon information provided by Splunk reports to ensure effective collaboration on ongoing projects and issue resolution.

In summary, the relationship between (C人员, B客户) is characterized by comprehensive maintenance activities that cover both routine operations and troubleshooting specific technical issues. C人员 works closely with other team members and utilizes tools like Splunk for reporting and coordination purposes to provide a robust level of support and service to B客户.&lt;SEP&gt;C personnel is involved in the maintenance activities for B客戶's systems.&lt;SEP&gt;B客戶接受來自C人員和其他工程師的維護和支持。&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provided technical maintenance support for B客戶, specifically addressing a Splunk Indexer Queue Full incident.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員also supports B客戶through various engineering tasks and maintenance activities.&lt;SEP&gt;C personnel resolves issues related to B客户的系统维护。&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provides maintenance support for B客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">client service,collaboration,engineering support,issue resolution,maintenance,maintenance activity,maintenance engineer,maintenance support,maintenance tasks,reporting,responsibility,service provision,support,support role,technical service,technical support</data>
