<edge source="B客戶" target="A人員">
  <data key="d7">13.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(A人員, B客戶) refers to a relationship where A人員 (the handling engineer or personnel) performs various maintenance tasks and activities on behalf of B客戶's systems as part of regular upkeep. The maintenance records of B客戶 contain the details of tasks and operations carried out by A人員, including updates provided when necessary. These duties encompass multiple specific tasks and are aimed at ensuring that B客户的 systems remain in optimal working condition through ongoing technical support and routine checks. Additionally, A人員 is responsible for conducting maintenance activities to ensure system reliability and performance, while also providing the required technical assistance to address any issues or requests from B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B客戶接受來自A人員和其他工程師的維護和支持。&lt;SEP&gt;A人員provides engineering support and executes maintenance tasks for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A personnel performs maintenance tasks for B客户's systems.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員maintains and provides support for B客户的systems according to their maintenance records.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員conducted maintenance activities on behalf of B客戶.</data>
