<edge source="B人員" target="C客戶">
  <data key="d7">18.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B人员, C客户) represents a relationship where B人员 (personnel) provide comprehensive maintenance services to C客户 (customers). The primary responsibilities of B人员 encompass various activities including resolving maintenance issues, conducting vulnerability patching and configuration updates, performing Splunk驻点服务 (Splunk on-site service), executing authorization checks, monitoring server performance, and ensuring overall system stability. Additionally, they assist in addressing specific technical incidents such as the Splunk SH abnormal hanging incident, highlighting their role not only in general maintenance but also in troubleshooting particular problems. B人员 are dedicated to offering support through continuous updates to ensure optimal functioning of systems used by C客户. These services are delivered consistently throughout the specified period and may involve on-site presence for direct service provision.&lt;SEP&gt;B人员为C客户提供了Splunk驻点服务。&lt;SEP&gt;B人員provided maintenance services for C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is responsible for providing maintenance services to C客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">activity execution,issue resolution,maintenance,maintenance handling,maintenance service,maintenance support,maintenance task execution,maintenance tasks,maintenance work,responsibility,service delivery,service provision,technical support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f8775862e3b8ea072578967e7520445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15d6c505e6a20b598aa21d52b466adcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe3f974e54dd1f1ad98289cc79980d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359</data>
